Title: Tokyo Auto Salon 2018: Lexani Wheels Japan Tour
Description:
WATCH IN 4K!

From Tokyo, to Yokohama,  to Chiba, and beyond. 

You may be thinking, "Hey LEXANI... What gives? This event happened in January."

Rather than post some half-hearted coverage shot on an i-phone X we wanted to take you to the show and beyond in this edit. We want you to see the owner's meet, where we gathered over 2 dozen vehicles, from all over the country. We came home with 500 gb of footage this year, and we wanted to bring you guys the best possible cut of it. 

We hope you enjoy it.

THANK YOU TO ALL OF OUR OWNERS AND SHOPS!
みんなありがとう!!
